{"title":"哀哉尼克松","authors":["禾君"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":5,"day":10}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"哀哉尼克松"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"禾君"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国副总统，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大名尼克松，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拉丁美洲去“旅行”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“后院”逞威风。（注）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"先到乌拉圭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又到阿根廷……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“美国骗子滚回去！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到处嘘骂声。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前天在秘鲁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“访问”大学生，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学生先给闭门羹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"然后石头扔。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"副官牙齿落，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总统脖子肿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保镖警察不敢动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"威风影无踪！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家中危机凶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“后院”乱哄哄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"船破又遇顶头风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哀哉尼克松！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"注：美国人把拉丁美洲叫做美国的“后院”。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}